jltl2dstar

Class SafraTreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • jltl2dstar.SafraTreeNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<SafraTreeNode>

    public class SafraTreeNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<SafraTreeNode>
    A node in a SafraTree. Each node has:
    - a name/id (integer)
    - a final flag (bool)
    - a parent (NULL for root node)
    - an older brother (NULL if node is oldest)
    - a younger brother (NULL if node is youngest)
    - an oldestChild (NULL if node has no children
    - a youngestChild (NULL if node has no children
    - a label (BitSet) for the powerset
